    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335040/extras/1b090d092cec89601f5061aef0d6f2e8.avif?t=1752765404\" width=800 height=73 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After a cataclysmic event, Valoria has fallen into despair. Mysterious powers have taken over and now controls the kingdom, spreading its influence to every corner and bending it to its will. When the raid that killed your family and destroyed your home left you with nothing, it ignited a burning desire for revenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335040/extras/da530fb4d46944b0f5a464fb9094f74f.avif?t=1752765404\" width=800 height=73 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The path to victory is paved in blood. Slash, dash and kill your way through countless enemies and powerful bosses with fast paced combat, special abilities, and fluid movement mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335040/extras/340e3685878f75ff593ca7d38ad4b892.avif?t=1752765404\" width=800 height=73 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on main quests and side quests which shape the world around you. Meet a cast of characters each with their own stories and motives, and leave your mark on Valoria as you uncover the truth behind its collapse. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335040/extras/a05ffa1628b33e195b51412758d7a153.avif?t=1752765404\" width=800 height=73 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once, you had a family. Once, this kingdom thrived. Now, all that remains is a dying land and a heart full of retribution. Rise from the ashes. Valoria’s fate rests in your hands.</p>",
